<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=JetBrains+Mono:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400;1,700&display=swap');

    * {
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono';
    }

    p {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #FFF;
      margin: 10px;
    }

    .mail {
      width: 500px;
      padding: 10px;
      min-height: 50vh;
      height: auto;
      justify-content: center;
      text-align: center;
      align-items: center;
      align-content: center;
      background-color: #0E0E0F;
    }

    .mail header {
      width:100%;
      padding: 10px;
    }

    .mail header h2 {
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #4A89DC;
      font-size: 32px;
    }

    .mail section {
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      padding: 10px;
    }

    .mail footer {
      padding: 10px;
      width: 100%;
    }

    .btn {
      padding: 5px;
      margin-top: 50px;
      color: #FFF;
      border-radius: 3px;
      background-color: #4A89DC;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <section class="mail">
    <header>
      <h2>Validação de email</h2>
    </header>
    <section>
      <p>Olá {{name}}, sejá bem vindo para validar seu email e realizar o log in, clique no link abaixo</p>
    </section>
    <footer>
      <a href="{{link}}auth/validation_mail/{{token}}" class="btn">Validar email</a>
    </footer>
  </section>
</body>
</html>